or a couple of hours thats about 144 plat. I believe 3 gems and the cash loot we split more than covers that.<br><br>Clerics need to be fair to the group and not be piggish and at the same time the group needs to make sure the cleric is compensated for her peridots.  <p>Caelie<BR>55 Human Cleric<BR>Proud Member of Eternal Haven<BR>Council Member<BR>" Crabcakes"<BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#575757><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/bemarr.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=boum>Boum</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 141<br> <font color=#E9D756>(2/20/02 6:07:20 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrdragonsandplanes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3073.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How much compensation do clerics require?</span><hr size=1> 4hrs = 12 dots (plus deaths if any) = 150 plat for someone with low cha. That's about the price of one quest gem... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ukerryndarkwater.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kerryn Darkwater</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 1072<br> <font color=#E9D756>(2/20/02 6:11:33 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrdragonsandplanes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3073.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How much compensation do clerics require?</span><hr size=1> Very simple. Clerics should count how many peridots they use during a grouping and multiply that by the cost. This should then be removed from the groups money and then the split should be done.<br><br>Giving them more or less really isnt on. <p><CENTER><A HREF="http://ak.lonelygamer.com"><IMG SRC="http://www.plattsflello.com/ryn.gif" BORDE